claim.claim-text:
1. A battery pack comprising: 
(a) a battery; 
(b) output terminals which are directly or indirectly connected to the battery electrodes; 
(c) a molding holder which is connected with the battery and also retains the output terminals; and 
(d) a molded plastic resin region which inserts and molds at least the battery and the molding holder and its connecting region, exposes the surfaces of the output terminals to the outside, and also joins the battery, the output terminals, and the molding holder as a single unit.
